This is a port of the RubyForge codebase to Rails.  It's about time!

We'll migrate existing data over; e.g., we're not tied to current rubyforge schema

What domain data will we keep? (see table listing in doc/rubyforge_tables.txt)
User
Membership
Group
Project
Forum
Message
NewsByte (would be good to decouple this from Forums)
MailingList
Tracker (currently this is artifact)
TrackerCannedResponse
TrackerCategory
TrackerCountsAgg

TrackerItem
Role
FrsPackage
FrsRelease
FrsFile
Trove

Leave behind (?)
ApiRequests
ActivityLog
Mirror


Architecture:
Apache, Rails, Memcached, Redis, Resque, PostgreSQL
